{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b1",
      "translation": "AIA is a trusted partner for our customers, enabling them to focus on financial security and family protection with peace of mind. Despite the far-reaching impact of COVID-19"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b2",
      "translation": "pandemic, I am deeply grateful to our employees, agents and partners for adapting to new ways of working and ensuring uninterrupted support to our customers"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b5",
      "translation": "Since the onset of the pandemic, our business teams have responded swiftly and actively worked to mitigate impact on our communities while ensuring employee safety. The Group has"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b6",
      "translation": "implemented comprehensive measures, including financial support, medical supplies, complimentary coverage, healthcare access, streamlined service processes and"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b7",
      "translation": "accelerated claims payments, which I am proud of. We continue to find every reason to pay claims, and during the year we paid out over USD 16 billion in insurance benefits and claims,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b9",
      "translation": "Although measures to contain COVID-19 resulted in new business value declining to USD 2.765 billion, as movement restrictions eased, sales momentum turned positive and"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b10",
      "translation": "gathered very strong momentum in 2021, with new business value in the first two months growing 15% year-on-year. Our large and growing in-force portfolio generates high-quality and recurring"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b11",
      "translation": "income streams, driving a 5% increase in operating profit after tax in 2020, while free surplus generated during the period grew 7%. As at 31 December 2020, embedded value equity reached USD 67.2 billion, and the Group's local capital aggregation method coverage ratio stood at 374%, demonstrating"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b13",
      "translation": "our strong capital position and prudent financial management."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b15",
      "translation": "policy, enabling the Group to capture future growth opportunities while maintaining financial flexibility."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b16",
      "translation": "AIA possesses distinctive competitive advantages that set us apart in a highly competitive market. With decades of operations in Asia, we have an unparalleled platform in the region and hold"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b17",
      "translation": "leading positions in most of our markets. Our consistent focus exclusively on Asia enables us to capture growth opportunities across the world's most attractive life insurance region. This focus,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b18",
      "translation": "combined with our leadership team's extensive Asia experience and workforce quality, has been a key driver of our strong performance."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b19",
      "translation": "Our unparalleled distribution strength enables direct customer engagement and delivery of high-quality professional advice to meet substantial and growing long-term protection and savings needs of Asian consumers. AIA has a market-leading brand"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b20",
      "translation": "built on the purpose of helping people live healthier, longer, better lives."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b22",
      "translation": "We aim to position AIA at the forefront of technology application globally, strengthen interconnectivity, expand scale and enhance efficiency. Deeper data analytics insights enable"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b23",
      "translation": "us to create unique and personalized customer experiences. Products and services aligned with individual needs and lifestyles have transformed public perception of life insurance,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b24",
      "translation": "laying a solid foundation for building long-term relationships with our customers."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b25",
      "translation": "Although 2020 was unprecedented, I am more optimistic than ever about Asia's life insurance industry prospects and AIA's future. We continue to challenge ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b26",
      "translation": "develop our priorities, and ensure we appropriately meet evolving customer expectations and financial needs. Our new corporate strategy is built on"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p13_b27",
      "translation": "AIA's existing strengths, advancing our transformation to deliver the best service to customers in the future."
    }
  ]
}
```
